### Register User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "recruiter@company.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "company": "Tech Corp"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "recruiter@company.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Verify Email (use token from register response in dev mode)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "VERIFICATION_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Get Profile (replace TOKEN with access token from login)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "recruiter@company.com"
}

### Reset Password (use token from forgot-password response in dev mode)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "RESET_TOKEN_HERE",
  "password": "NewPassword123!"
}

